Pacifi3D (C) 2005 Fosters
=========================

2005-04-01: Pacifi3D 0.3
- Sound!
- Added support for extra romsets. Pacifi3D now supports:
   puckman
   puckmana
   puckmanf
   puckmod
   pacman
   pacmanf
   pacmod
   hangly
   hangly2
   hangly3
   newpuckx
  Start Pacifi3D with:
    pacifi3d <romname>
  to run a different set. (defaults to puckman)
- Started work on ghost eyes


2005-01-17: Pacifi3D 0.2
- Fixed fullscreen in windows.
- Made turning in first person view rotate slower.
  (i.e. no longer snaps straight to new direction)
- Chase View.
- Classic View.
- Keys Rotate in First person views (but joystick doesnt yet)
- MacOSX Makefile (but no builds released yet so roll your own)
- Other misc code cleanups.


2005-01-09: Pacifi3D 0.1
- Initial Releaase
